Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.21,0:02:52.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All the pirates who are \Nafter the One Piece...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.75,0:02:57.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...head for the New World,\Nthe second half of the Grand Line.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.93,0:03:07.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}However, no one has ever fully explored it\Nexcept for Gold Roger, King of the Pirates.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.31,0:03:13.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The New World has ruined\Nmany pirates' dreams and ambitions.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.36,0:03:16.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now, Monkey D. Luffy,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.37,0:03:20.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a boy whose body turned to rubber \Nafter he ate the Gum-Gum Fruit,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.61,0:03:22.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and his friends venture into that sea.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.99,0:03:26.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna become the King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.87,0:03:33.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To take down one of the Four Emperors -\Nthe rulers of the New World,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.38,0:03:36.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Luffy and the others formed a \Npirate alliance with Trafalgar Law
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.45,0:03:38.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and have come to Dressrosa.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.47,0:03:43.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Law, Doflamingo, and his brother Corazon.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.27,0:03:47.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Their relationship began years ago...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.37,0:03:50.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look! It's the Op-Op Fruit!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.94,0:03:55.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Now, eat it! Here! Eat it quickly!\N--What are you doing...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.32,0:03:57.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gross!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.23,0:04:03.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There! Chew it like this!\NChew it up and swallow it down!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.80,0:04:09.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It must be Corazon!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.83,0:04:14.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If he's there, don't let him go anywhere!\NHe has the Op-Op Fruit!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.24,0:04:20.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have nowhere to run.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.47,0:04:26.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Maybe I can let Law get away, just him...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.15,0:04:31.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have no chance to survive now but...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.77,0:04:35.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}will you remember me even after I die?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.73,0:04:39.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll die with a smile so...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.03,0:04:48.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Because... if you think of me someday,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.59,0:04:54.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'd rather you remember my smile.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.70,0:05:01.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Law, we gotta get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.64,0:05:10.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.69,0:05:19.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"Advance, Law!\NThe Kindhearted Man's Final Fight!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.70,0:05:26.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Don't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.75,0:05:30.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what's going on!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.74,0:05:34.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suddenly, the town is surrounded by\Nsome kind of a giant cage!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.89,0:05:36.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't get in!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.72,0:05:38.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And as hard as it is to believe,\Nin the cage,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.79,0:05:43.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it seems the pirates had a falling out\Nand they're killing each other!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.49,0:05:46.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Drie!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.05,0:05:50.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you going? Help me!\NCan't you do something about the cage?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.53,0:05:52.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Don't go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.73,0:05:59.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an enemy raid!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.69,0:06:06.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the Donquixote Family!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.06,0:06:08.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Drie!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.67,0:06:11.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! Where did that brat go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.67,0:06:14.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He isn't there when I need him the most!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.29,0:06:19.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's stronger than anybody but has no guts!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.26,0:06:32.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doflamingo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.05,0:06:35.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was you guys who stole \Nthe Op-Op Fruit, wasn't it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.60,0:06:38.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it were so,\NI wouldn't have to go through all this!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.09,0:06:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you let it be stolen,\Nyou drunken idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.53,0:06:50.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a treasure house-{\i1}in{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.52,0:06:54.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, carry all the treasures out carefully!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.39,0:06:57.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is great-{\i1}in{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.46,0:07:01.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not bad, not bad!\NThey've got quite a lot!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.38,0:07:07.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop fooling around, you guys!\NLook for Corazon!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.52,0:07:12.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Buffalo!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.17,0:07:14.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How's your search from up there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.10,0:07:25.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all burnt - I don't think \Nthere are any survivors-{\i1}dasuyan{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.80,0:07:26.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bzz...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.91,0:07:28.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I picked up a message!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.82,0:07:31.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We took a boy into protective \Ncustody at the coast.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.20,0:07:33.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll keep searching to see \Nif there are other victims!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.95,0:07:38.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They said the Navy took someone\Ninto protective custody!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.41,0:07:43.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?!\NGet your lazy ass in gear and find Corazon!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.13,0:07:44.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Oh, Okay!\N--Okay-{\i1}dasuyan{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.25,0:07:48.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Corazon, that fool...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.53,0:07:50.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is he hiding?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.13,0:07:55.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or has he already dropped dead?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.71,0:08:07.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Doffy. This is our boss.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.92,0:08:11.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone got knocked out?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.94,0:08:14.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That must be "Haki"!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.37,0:08:18.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother, don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.12,0:08:20.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.77,0:08:25.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you also take away the power I had?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.84,0:08:32.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want me to give you...\Nthe strength to take revenge?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.02,0:08:37.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't undo what you've done now!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.23,0:08:42.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going back to the Holyland\Nby taking your head!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.54,0:08:51.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doflamingo. Rosinante.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.63,0:08:55.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry that you had to have...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.07,0:08:58.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...a father like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.72,0:09:41.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.37,0:09:45.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.93,0:09:48.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think they found Corazon!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.14,0:09:54.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Law. This is a blind spot for the pirates.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.41,0:09:57.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They'll never find you. Stay still!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.70,0:10:00.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Corazon went that way!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.10,0:10:03.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lao G! This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.88,0:10:09.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Come on! Follow me!\N--I'll crush you-{\i1}in{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.65,0:10:13.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh? I can't open it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.17,0:10:15.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Something is on it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.99,0:10:18.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Cora-san!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.56,0:10:20.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you aiming at?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.89,0:10:28.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Corazon!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.87,0:10:31.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vipera Glaive!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.31,0:10:47.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Corazon!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.35,0:10:51.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sticky Launcher!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.63,0:11:09.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.87,0:11:14.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Diamante!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.80,0:11:16.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.98,0:11:33.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.75,0:11:53.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You jerk!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.06,0:11:55.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why have you been pretending \Nthat you can't talk?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.13,0:12:02.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I got nothing to talk about...\Nwith you fools.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.18,0:12:03.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Screw you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.01,0:12:07.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you make a fool of the Young Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.64,0:12:10.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's unforgivable! I won't forgive you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.25,0:12:16.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's too much, Gladius!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.90,0:12:19.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He'll die before the Young Master gets here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.49,0:12:24.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.72,0:12:30.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was trying to force an all-out war\Nbetween us and the Navy today!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.77,0:12:34.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a sinful bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.97,0:12:44.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Cora-san!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.22,0:12:46.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! The Young Master's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.58,0:13:18.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been six months.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.62,0:13:22.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Corazon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.68,0:14:11.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Young Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.30,0:14:31.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have no place to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.74,0:14:35.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, do you wanna come with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.59,0:14:55.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Marine Code 01746.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.88,0:15:00.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Commander Rosinante of\Nthe Navy Headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.16,0:15:06.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Donquixote Family, captain, Doflamingo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.27,0:15:13.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have been undercover\Nto prevent a future tragedy of your doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.99,0:15:16.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am a Navy soldier!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.22,0:15:33.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry that I lied you...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.43,0:15:38.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I lied because I didn't want you to hate me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.37,0:15:43.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why are you bringing it up now?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.06,0:15:45.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I already...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.19,0:15:48.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...knew it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.92,0:15:54.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You fool! Do you think it'll help you\Nto apologize now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.47,0:15:57.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop telling those insipid jokes and...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.95,0:16:00.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...answer these two questions!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.71,0:16:03.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's the Op-Op Fruit?! Where's Law?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.89,0:16:07.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Devil Fruit...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.67,0:16:12.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Op-Op Fruit... I let Law eat it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.67,0:16:15.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a Devil Fruit eater now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.53,0:16:19.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He managed to get out of the cage.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.64,0:16:22.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet he's been taken into protective custody
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.95,0:16:25.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,by a look-out ship from the Navy HQ by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.25,0:16:27.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't touch him now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.53,0:16:34.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Young Master-{\i1}sama{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.41,0:16:38.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We heard the Navy said on the radio earlier\Nthey took a boy under their care!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.02,0:16:41.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you report that sooner?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.21,0:16:46.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I rushed here even if I don't look like it-{\i1}dasuyan{\i0}!\N--I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.04,0:16:48.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A boy?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.67,0:16:51.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What a strange coincidence!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.18,0:16:53.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Law is here!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.04,0:17:04.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Check into that quickly!\NI'll undo the Birdcage!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.25,0:17:07.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is an unbelievably great coincidence!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.99,0:17:12.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As I thought, Law,\Nsomething compels you to stay alive.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.74,0:17:18.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Saviors keep descending upon you\None after another.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.94,0:17:21.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prepare to set sail!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.11,0:17:25.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If what he said was true,\Nwe'll sink the Navy's look-out ship
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.50,0:17:27.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and get Law back!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.25,0:17:29.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.94,0:17:31.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would you wanna go after Law?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.67,0:17:35.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would I wanna go after Law?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.63,0:17:38.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he ate the Op-Op Fruit,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.57,0:17:44.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he needs to be educated \Nin order to die for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.98,0:17:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boy... You've done tons \Nof unnecessary things!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.27,0:17:52.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you wanna get in my way?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.82,0:17:57.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do I have to kill another \Nmember of my biological family?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.32,0:18:01.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Cora-san, are you sure you'll be alright?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.58,0:18:10.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know you can't shoot me...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.56,0:18:14.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so much like your father!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.51,0:18:16.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You told me you'll be alright,\Ndidn't you?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.09,0:18:20.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Listen, Law.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.96,0:18:23.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Pirates can't resist taking treasure boxes
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.86,0:18:26.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to their ships whenever they find them.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.88,0:18:30.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That means if you stay in here,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.36,0:18:33.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you'll definitely have a chance \Nto get out of the cage.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.06,0:18:34.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\NDon't miss it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.53,0:18:35.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about you, Cora-{\i1}san{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.65,0:18:39.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You silly...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.07,0:18:42.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doffy wants you and the Op-Op power.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.42,0:18:45.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doffy and I are brothers by blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.42,0:18:51.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, he'd get pissed at me\Nbut I'm sure he won't kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.11,0:18:53.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.82,0:19:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This will cause anything you interact with\Nto not make any noise.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.49,0:19:03.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, see you in the next town.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.64,0:19:04.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Law.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.56,0:19:09.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.11,0:19:23.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This isn't what you told me, Cora-san!\NYou said he won't kill you!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.91,0:19:30.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Law won't obey you! Doffy...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.32,0:19:34.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Affected by White Lead Disease,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.16,0:19:38.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he was doomed to die in three years.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.28,0:19:41.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he got over it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.35,0:19:45.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's not the same Law...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.72,0:19:50.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...who lost track of himself and came \Nto visit a crazy pirate that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.14,0:19:57.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is nothing he can gain from you\Nsince you're like a child of destruction!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.57,0:19:59.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave him alone now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.11,0:20:02.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He is free!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.04,0:20:28.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say it again!\NWho did you call a monster?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.68,0:20:32.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! He tripped\Nand he's on fire at the same time!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.39,0:20:35.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--See? You had a quiet sleep, didn't you?!\N--Cut it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.85,0:21:17.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.95,0:21:30.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Not yet...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.19,0:21:36.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm gonna stay alive for a little bit more...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.14,0:21:41.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pull the ship over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.70,0:21:44.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Because if I die now...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.53,0:21:49.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}the spell I cast on you \Nwill be broken instantly...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.85,0:21:53.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and your voice and noise you make...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.46,0:21:57.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...will be heard throughout the island.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.50,0:22:00.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Go, Law...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.82,0:22:04.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Quietly... without being noticed...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.03,0:22:07.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Go farther... and farther...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.87,0:22:11.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There is nothing to bind you down anymore...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.66,0:22:15.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Whether it's the iron border \Nbarrier of the White Town
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.49,0:22:17.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nor a short life expectancy...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.07,0:22:20.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Nothing and no one will limit you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.96,0:22:22.88,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,TSURU
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.46,0:22:26.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Tsuru's warship! Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.86,0:22:42.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You are...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.80,0:22:45.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...free now...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.06,0:22:54.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.94,0:23:29.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sacrificing his own life,\NCora-san paved Law's path to the future.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.30,0:23:34.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Law inherits his wish and \Nto become truly free,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.08,0:23:37.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}he fires a shot on behalf of Cora-san, who \Ncouldn't take a shot on that fateful day,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.06,0:23:38.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,aiming straight at Doflamingo!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.96,0:23:44.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!\N"To Be Free! Law's Injection Shot Blasts!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.10,0:23:46.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be the King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.21,0:23:48.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
